00:06:37.050 --> 00:06:38.750
you're, you know, young and naive,

00:06:39.780 --> 00:06:42.930
but the same people who do the enslaving

00:06:42.930 --> 00:06:45.270
are also often the same
people who start the state.

00:06:45.270 --> 00:06:47.670
And that's gonna be true
in our case as well, right?

00:06:47.670 --> 00:06:49.170
The people who are doing the enslaving

00:06:49.170 --> 00:06:50.670
are also gonna be the same people who,

00:06:50.670 --> 00:06:52.890
by the end of the story,
are gonna start the state.

00:06:52.890 --> 00:06:55.350
So there's a general story

00:06:55.350 --> 00:06:56.970
about causality here,

00:06:56.970 --> 00:06:58.290
