00:48:30.600 --> 00:48:32.490
which I hope you've been following,

00:48:32.490 --> 00:48:34.590
about how the creation of Ukraine

00:48:34.590 --> 00:48:36.213
is not about east and west.

00:48:37.089 --> 00:48:38.670
That's a much later point of view.

00:48:38.670 --> 00:48:40.650
But about south to north.

00:48:40.650 --> 00:48:43.440
It's about south to
north, and north to south,

00:48:43.440 --> 00:48:44.970
where south to north has to do

00:48:44.970 --> 00:48:47.790
with the ancient world, the Greeks,

00:48:47.790 --> 00:48:50.790
the Byzantines, the Black Sea,

