and the northern coast of the Black Sea,

00:48:52.710 --> 00:48:56.190
and things moving up towards Kyiv.

00:48:56.190 --> 00:48:58.710
And now the north to south has to do

00:48:58.710 --> 00:49:00.900
with the Vikings.

00:49:00.900 --> 00:49:04.530
They're moving down the Dnipro
River, seeking Byzantium.

00:49:04.530 --> 00:49:06.240
And the Kyivan state, you know,

00:49:06.240 --> 00:49:08.520
putting it very grandly,
is a kind of encounter

00:49:08.520 --> 00:49:09.870
of a movement from north to south,

00:49:09.870 --> 00:49:11.940
and another movement from south to north,

00:49:11.940 --> 00:49:13.620
which meet each other in the city

00:49:13.620 --> 00:49:15.360
which already existed and was dominated

00:49:15.360 --> 00:49:18.390
at the time by the Khazars.

