because it's important,

00:49:51.630 --> 00:49:53.700
the weakness of this system.

00:49:53.700 --> 00:49:54.690
And it's important, also,

00:49:54.690 --> 00:49:56.820
when you think about the heritage of Rus'

00:49:56.820 --> 00:49:59.730
and people who claim the
heritage of Rus' today,

00:49:59.730 --> 00:50:02.370
the weakness of the system was
the principle of succession,

00:50:02.370 --> 00:50:04.380
or the absence of a
principle of succession.

00:50:04.380 --> 00:50:05.880
There was no idea that, for example,

00:50:05.880 --> 00:50:08.430
the oldest son would inherit
or anything like that.

00:50:09.330 --> 00:50:11.250
Basically, parts of Rus' were given out

00:50:11.250 --> 00:50:12.840
to various sons,

00:50:12.840 --> 00:50:15.420
and there tended to be lots of sons.

00:50:15.420 --> 00:50:18.090
Volodymyr managed to keep
seven different districts

00:50:18.090 --> 00:50:20.403
under his control by wit,

00:50:21.450 --> 00:50:23.490
but it wasn't simple, this
business of having sons.

